history.content:
Hi all, 


There are some outdated lists online that do not include CS 169. While we work with campus partners to remove those links, please review the information below: 

Drop a Class
To drop an enrolled or wait-listed class from your schedule, go to your current class schedule and select the class you wish to drop. You must confirm the transaction before the class can be dropped from your schedule. Please be aware some courses have early drop deadlines (EDD, PDF). The deadline for dropping EDD courses is midnight on Friday of the second week of instruction. Check your college/school's website for more information.

A $10 fee is charged for each class dropped after the second week of instruction.
